First off, this game is ad free and IAP free. The game has a surprising amount of depth for a mobile game. You level up your characters and can pick their stat growth. You can also equip mod chips which further modify the character. When you go into a shop you can flip through boxes looking for a character hidden in the back shelf! Can't wait to see all the characters in the game. Make sure to play with the sound on as they have the TTG voice actors and George Takei!
